{
  "stem": "25639.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then, my father called us together and said that we have to leave tomorrow morning, and we don't know where we are going, but that we will hide the family jewelry, which was our investment.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so, that we should all know the hiding places, these-- that this would-- we can always turn this jewelry into cash when we would come back home.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But what we didn't know is that we might never return.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That night, my father and my brothers dug a hole under the hardwood floor in one of our bedrooms, and they placed a metal box under this hardwood floor, and replaced the hardwood as naturally as it was possible.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "On top of it was furniture, and actually, it was a wash stand that was on top of it, with towels.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And sure enough, at 5:00 in the morning came the knock on the door.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we were-- all-- we all had to go to city hall where already other Jewish families were waiting.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When all the Jews were rounded up in [? north ?] Berehy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We were driven in a truck to the neighboring city called Beregszasz, the provincial capital.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "At first, we were taken to the beautiful synagogue in Beregszasz while the Nazis were setting up a ghetto in the brick factory called the [INAUDIBLE] Teglagyar.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That means-- [INAUDIBLE] was the name of the owner.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Teglagyar means brick factory.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And there they amassed thousands and thousands of Jews from the entire province of Berehy [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "End of tape two.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
